720242f-a.title: Manhattan: Greenwich Street - Barrow Street
720242f-a.text:
Greenwich Street, south from but not including Barrow Street, as seen from the United States Government Warehouse and Stores, and showing a general view of lower Manhattan. The Ninth Ave., Elevated appears on
Greenwich Street.
July 25, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
